{"tid":1175094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛油果核變「膠餐具」，半年可自行分解夠環保","createTime":"2019-05-28T10:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T06:37:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":668,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"efa6144b4a6c02bb09b8707556cc7eec2b0aab8a","tid":1175094,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2360000/2362800/niu02--_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2360000%2F2362800%2Fniu02--_1024.jpg&h=3dd9ed7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年愈來愈多人喜歡食牛油果，但想不到當中的牛油果核除了種植之外，還有其他用途。這間墨西哥公司就利用牛油果核物質降解速度比塑膠快的特性，推出由牛油果核製成的生物塑料餐具，希望能取代現時的塑膠餐具！<br />\n<br />\n【相關報道】手搖杯「FLOAT」設計爆紅！無飲管也可讓杯底珍珠一粒不剩<br />\n<br />\n【相關報道】【剪完再駁】環保 RenewCable USB 線眾籌！壞線簡單 DIY 更換<br />\n<br />\n墨西哥公司創辦人 Scott Mung&iacute;a 畢業於化學工程系，他在校時就花了 3 年多時閒研究牛油果核，結果發現牛油果核物質降解的速度比起塑膠快很多。於是，他嘗試利用牛油果核轉化成生物塑料（Bioplastics），取得專利後命名為「Avoplast」。Avoplast 製成的餐具外表像一般的即棄塑膠餐具，然而最快能夠在 240 天内完全分解，比起塑膠餐具要環保得多。<br />\n<br />\n現時，「Avoplast」推出了刀叉、匙羹以及飲管，只要放在乾爽地方就能保存一年。「Avoplast」產品主要在拉丁美洲銷售，不過大家也可在官網買得到。US$9.89（約 HK$77）能買到 150 支 Avoplast 飲管，平均約 HK$0.5 一支；US$7.49（約 HK$58）則買到 24 支 Avoplast 餐具，平均為 HK$2.5 一支，不算十分貴。有興趣的朋友不妨入手支持吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6_NnIHCHIgs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6_NnIHCHIgs&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=f7bd5d5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6_NnIHCHIgs</a><br />\n牛油果核製成的「Avoplast」餐具看起來像一般塑膠餐具，但只需大半年就能自行分解。<br />\n<br />\n「Avoplast」 比起塑膠餐具要環保得多，減塑之餘能減廢。"},{"pid":"c772118282d8940de03fee588a5319e2ccbde446","tid":1175094,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2362800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2362800&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=fd6e48e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2362800</a>"},{"pid":"fb9bec32d8877cbc3d60d2d23e9e098431ed8059","tid":1175094,"uid":84212,"like":784,"dislike":4,"score":780,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95f791cc21a72a91ba879cfb155b4b6133208e7f","tid":1175094,"uid":164050,"like":41,"dislike":386,"score":-345,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e875dd5cdae58f626e6090965e3bf0a769929a35","tid":1175094,"uid":220701,"like":187,"dislike":1,"score":186,"quote":{"pid":"95f791cc21a72a91ba879cfb155b4b6133208e7f","tid":1175094,"uid":164050,"like":41,"dislike":386,"score":-345,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:37:10.000Z","msg":"有話無視咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7e038d2273e5d16fa1cf5ca54adc6ab7a0953a","tid":1175094,"uid":15880,"like":305,"dislike":0,"score":305,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"天啟四騎士:<br />\n<br />\n環境就係要reduce !<br />\n<br />\n市民:<br />\n咁reuse, recyle 呢?<br />\n<br />\n騎士: ridicules !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df91ff27ce45f37f9cf0284cbcb0103fc86cc1a","tid":1175094,"uid":239384,"like":108,"dislike":2,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:41:16.000Z","msg":"幾好幾好 但係好貴下(對比一般膠餐具) 肯轉用嘅人應該比較少 希望之後可以進一步降低成本降低價格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前有隻小麥？做嘅飲管 用完可以煮黎食極有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f94980dc86675f10b31754a24a1f8c6a01bb5a2","tid":1175094,"uid":153239,"like":134,"dislike":0,"score":134,"quote":{"pid":"95f791cc21a72a91ba879cfb155b4b6133208e7f","tid":1175094,"uid":164050,"like":41,"dislike":386,"score":-345,"citedBy":14,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:34:23.000Z","msg"