/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c85488d35ce2d605db1838d8b461f139930881","tid":1175094,"uid":55194,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"呢D就真環保<br />\n香港果班,行撚開啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7145eb1f9e09d881dc1028b5738b3af039b9c1b2","tid":1175094,"uid":47496,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"5f7e038d2273e5d16fa1cf5ca54adc6ab7a0953a","tid":1175094,"uid":15880,"like":305,"dislike":0,"score":305,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"天啟四騎士:<br />\n<br />\n環境就係要reduce !<br />\n<br />\n市民:<br />\n咁reuse, recyle 呢?<br />\n<br />\n騎士: ridicules !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"市民：我哋可以用鐵<br />\n騎士：Ironic!!!"},{"pid":"e1b4bf2dfc4ecd53963d44fa5689fc4d03c5c442","tid":1175094,"uid":197196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"環保撚未日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d436315220922a4038f758406efa3ecd96e0e984","tid":1175094,"uid":34013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:53:34.000Z","msg":"$58 24支都不算十分貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e18278733e473df72e8cdc7860e350ff94396c3","tid":1175094,"uid":145472,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:56:21.000Z","msg":"4個月前我都整咗條片，<br />\n講十種傳統塑膠嘅替代品<br />\n（下面有link ，但唔想俾 view 我的話可以無視，重點我會而家寫出黎）<br />\n<br />\n十大之中，牛油果果核，<br />\n我只係放第九位。<br />\n<br />\n大家要小心，<br />\n商家話「半年可分解」，<br />\n要睇清楚佢「喺咩環境下分解」。<br />\n<br />\n以我所知，<br />\n佢呢種生物塑膠，係要喺「高溫高濕度嘅工業埋肥環境」下，先會分解得咁快。<br />\n<br />\n如果喺堆填區，或者海入面，<br />\n都要兩三年先分解。<br />\n<br />\n環唔環保，就睇你睇重咩。<br />\n係佢分唔分解到，<br />\n定係會唔會放毒素，<br />\n定係原材料是否可再生，<br />\n定係會唔會插親海龜個鼻。<br />\n<br />\n但肯定嘅係，佢貴過傳統塑膠。<br />\n<br />\n只係分享下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BmOxnJg67tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBmOxnJg67tw&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=468691e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BmOxnJg67tw</a><br />\n<br />\n不入十大：<br />\n第十二位：唔用飲管<br />\n第十一位：可重用飲管（例如不銹鋼，玻璃，矽膠，竹）<br />\n<br />\n十大塑膠飲管替代品：<br />\n第十位：粟米塑膠飲管（PLA生物塑膠）<br />\n第九位：牛油果果核 / 甘蔗渣纖維塑膠飲管 （PLA生物塑膠）<br />\n第八位：糖和植物油發酵製成的 PHA 生物塑膠飲管<br />\n第七位：紙飲管<br />\n第六位：植物莖部（例：小麥莖，木瓜葉，通心菜）<br />\n第五位：糖飲管<br />\n第四位：餅乾飲管<br />\n第三位：意粉飲管<br />\n第二位：大米木薯飲管<br />\n第一位：海藻飲管"},{"pid":"3ae32ae3319c4fc387c4a12531c2207572095aee","tid":1175094,"uid":144594,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"cd1f7d91d2203d9f42d38b2f60c1d245bcf5e0bc","tid":1175094,"uid":13467,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"quote":{"pid":"a93f6604763bda40ba4859e60e23e03a62fabf0c","tid":1175094,"uid":162866,"like":8,"dislike":63,"score":-55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"我就係中意用膠啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n環保撚死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T11:16:36.000Z","msg":"你係咪以為自己好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲擺明係憤世小學雞大個左變左人格障礙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a784ff7849340abbf0e24ab66ce0914e88e8594d","tid":1175094,"uid":87428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:09:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k-cavEKkirc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk-cavEKkirc&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2F3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=2e7bbdb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k-cavEKkirc</a>"},{"pid":"8e2c580cad8e32c9df6b2fb7b50cbd19883f5e32","tid":1175094,"uid":108022,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:12:16